o:MethodTargetItem.a:MethodScript: Sub %Method%(obj) Dim objChild For Each objChild In obj.Children WriteDebug("Found child of type: " & objChild.ClassKind) If (objChild.ClassKind = PdLDM.cls_Model) Then WriteDebug("Found LDM: " & objChild.Name) End If Next End Sub
